messages.title: Fiona will put you first!
messages.content: "I have worked hard all my life and had more bad times than I care to remember so I know how difficult it is for many folk now. What I have learned is how to get things done and how to improve life for more people than just myself."

leaflet.personalStatement: "I have worked hard all my life and had more bad times than I care to remember so I know how difficult it is for many folk now. What I have learned is how to get things done and how to improve life for more people than just myself."
leaflet.additionalNotes: The leaflet encourages people to get in touch with the candidate and provides various contact methods. It is an election communication for the specified constituency and date.
